    "headline": "2026 國際錦標賽 - 邀請及公開資格賽",
    "posttime": 1779766203,
    "updatetime": 1779766203,
    "body": [
      "[img]{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/3703047/1477d1a3748ef268c4b431dd4af64cf4ad8ffdd7.png[/img]",
      "[p]這一年來，世界各地的 Dota 戰隊不斷奮戰，以證明自己值得獲得直接邀請參與國際錦標賽——在世界最大舞台上爭奪冠軍神盾的機會。 獲得邀請的戰隊可開始專注於最後的準備工作，而其餘的競爭者則要面對爭取參賽資格的最後機會。[/p]",
      "[h3]直接邀請名單[/h3]",
      "[p]距離大賽開幕還有不到三個月的時間，我們很高興向以下七支戰隊發出邀請，前往中國上海參加 2026 年國際錦標賽：[/p]",
      "[list]",
      "[*]Aurora Gaming",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Egor \"Nightfall\" Grigorenko",
      "Rafli \"Mikoto\" Fathur Rahman",
      "Wei Shen \"Ws`\" Chung",
      "Myroslav \"Mira\" Kolpakov",
      "Oleh \"kaori\" Medvedok",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]BoomBoys",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Ilia \"Kiritych~\" Ulianov",
      "Danil \"gpk~\" Skutin",
      "Matvei \"MieRo`\" Vasiunin",
      "Vitalie \"Save-\" Melnic",
      "Vladislav \"Kataomi`\" Semenov",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Team Falcons",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Oliver \"Skiter\" Lepko",
      "Stanislav \"Malr1ne\" Potorak",
      "Ammar \"ATF\" Alassaf",
      "Andreas \"Cr1t-\" Nielsen",
      "Jingjun \"Sneyking\" Wu",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Team Liquid",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Michael \"m1CKe\" Vu",
      "Michał \"Nisha\" Jankowski",
      "Marcus \"Ace\" Christensen",
      "Samuel \"Boxi\" Svahn",
      "Erik \"tOfu\" Engel",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Tundra Esports",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Ivan \"Pure\" Moskalenko",
      "Bozhidar \"bzm\" Bogdanov",
      "Neta \"33\" Shapira",
      "Matthew \"Ari\" Walker",
      "Matthew \"Whitemon\" Filemon",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Xtreme Gaming",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Chunyu \"Ame\" Wang",
      "Jin Xiang \"NothingToSay\" Cheng",
      "Jing \"Xxs\" Lin",
      "Linsen \"fy\" Xu",
      "Jian Wei \"xNova\" Yap",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Team Yandex",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Alimzhan \"医者watson\" Islambekov",
      "Ilya \"CHIRA_JUNIOR\" Chirtsov",
      "Dmitrii \"DM\" Dorokhin",
      "Martin \"Saksa\" Sazdov",
      "Arman \"Malady\" Orazbayev",
      "[/expand]",
      "[/list]",
      "[h3]地區資格賽[/h3][p]",
      "以上七支戰隊已經獲得了邀請，這意味著國際錦標賽還有九個席位，等待著那些能夠從地區資格賽嚴峻的考驗中突圍而出的戰隊。 今年，我們將東歐和西歐資格賽合併為一個歐洲資格賽，共有四個晉級席位。 完整時間表請見下方。[/p]",
      "[list][*][b]中國[/b]，6 月 15 日至 18 日（2 個席位）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Vici Gaming",
      "Roar Gaming",
      "Yakutou Brothers",
      "Team Resilience",
      "[b]（+4 支公開資格賽戰隊）[/b]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]南美[/b]，6 月 15 日至 19 日（1 個席位）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "LGD Gaming",
      "PlayTime",
      "Estar Backs",
      "Red Hot Chili Pibble",
      "Amaru Gaming",
      "Hokori",
      "[b]（+4 支公開資格賽戰隊）[/b]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]東南亞[/b]，6 月 19 日至 23 日（1 個席位）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "REKONIX",
      "OG",
      "Execration",
      "Team Nemesis",
      "GLYPH",
      "[b]（+5 支公開資格賽戰隊）[/b]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]歐洲[/b]，6 月 21 日至 28 日（4 個席位）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "TEAM VISION",
      "Team Spirit",
      "MOUZ",
      "Natus Vincere",
      "Nigma Galaxy",
      "Virtus.pro",
      "enjoy",
      "Power Rangers",
      "[b]（+8 支公開資格賽戰隊）[/b]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]北美[/b]，6 月 24 日至 26 日（1 個席位）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "GamerLegion",
      "[b]（+3 支公開資格賽戰隊）[/b]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[/list]",
      "[p]資格賽程於 6 月 28 日結束後，我們將確定完整的參賽名單，然後下一站就是上海。 小組賽將於 8 月 13 日至 16 日開打，採用為期 3 天的 5 輪瑞士制賽程，接著在週日進行五場淘汰賽。 剩下的八支戰隊將於 8 月 20 日至 23 日把比賽帶入體育館，於此爭奪冠軍神盾。[/p]"
